1. "*Čekaj* me ovde dok se ne vratim!" (Wait for me here until I come back!)
2. "*Čekala* je cele sate da dočeka njegov dolazak." (She waited for hours to welcome his arrival.)
3. "*Čekali* smo još jednu nedelju do početka školske godine." (We waited for one more week until the start of the school year.)
4. "*Čekaće* još mnogo godina da se ostvari njihov san." (They will have to wait for many more years to realize their dream.)
5. "*Čekajući* da joj se jave, čitala je knjigu." (While waiting for her to be contacted, she was reading a book.)